13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
15 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 3-180 of Title 70, unless there
16 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
17 A. The State Department of Education shall establish and
18 maintain the Oklahoma High Dosage Tutoring Program.
19 B. For the purposes of this section, “cohort” means a student
20 or group of students of no more than four (4) who receive subject-
21 specific high dosage tutoring in mathematics or reading in at least
22 three thirty-minute sessions each school week throughout a semester
23 by an individual employed or contracted as a high dosage tutor by a
24 public school district participating in the program.
